      },
      "id": "mark_1783402715865_zstu3",
      "text": "The algorithm is allowed to change values, move pointers, and update state, but this statement must be true again when the loop is ready for the next iteration.",
      "url": "https://algo.monster/problems/two_pointers_invariants"
    },
    {
