          "textOffset": 0
        }
      },
      "id": "mark_1783405859746_qo88y",
      "text": "That is what makes these problems feel different from opposite-direction scans. You are not searching from both sides. You are building the answer progressively as you sweep through the input.",
      "url": "https://algo.monster/problems/same_direction_family_map"
    },
    {
