          "textOffset": 0
        }
      },
      "id": "mark_1783406634540_pqjzk",
      "text": "As you go through the following problems, pay attention to one question:\n\nWhat does the region before the slow pointer mean right now?",
      "url": "https://algo.monster/problems/same_direction_family_map"
    },
    {
