          "parentTagName": "p",
          "textOffset": 0
        }
      },
      "id": "mark_1783574657317_zog71",
      "text": "Interestingly, binary search works beyond sorted arrays. You can use binary search whenever you make a binary decision to shrink the search range. We will see this in the following modules.",
      "url": "https://algo.monster/problems/binary_search_intro"
    },
    {
      "color": "#134515",
      "createdAt": 1783574734550,
      "highlightSource": {
        "endMeta": {
          "parentDomPath": [
            1,
            1,
            1,
